  "countermodel_guard": {
    "kernel": "phi_(1/10,1/1000)(u)=exp(-u^2-u^4/10-(cosh(4u)-1)/1000)*(1+u^4/10)",
    "certified_point": "x=21/5",
    "laguerre_ball": "[-0.000213478480591774964507646766853475076598648832979809 +/- 5.09E-55]",
    "deduction": "L(0)>0, the certified L(21/5)<0, and L(x)->0 imply that L'(y)>0 for some y>21/5. Thus uniform strong log-concavity, strict root-variable concavity, and theta-type decay do not imply the monotonicity target."
